at.ac.tuwien.infosys.jcloudscale.migration

Class MigrationReason

  • java.lang.Object
    • at.ac.tuwien.infosys.jcloudscale.migration.MigrationReason
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class MigrationReason
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Describes the reason why a migration request was triggered.

    The rules engine can create a MigrationReason object to describe why a migration request was triggered. Each method defined in IMigrationTrigger accepts an optional MigrationReason object as parameter which will than be stored inside the migration's MigrationDescriptor.
